 "lines": [
  {
   "i": 1,
   "en": "Ozaki"
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "Yes... yes, understood. No, please,"
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "I'm sorry for asking so much of you"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "Ah... Ms. Ozaki's on the phone"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "Yes, I hope we can work together"
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "again. Goodbye"
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "Who is she talking to?"
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "Haah..."
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "Um... Ms. Ozaki? What's wrong?"
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "Oh, Eri. You were here?"
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "Yeah, just now..."
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "You look down... Did something happen?"
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "A little something"
  },
  {
   "i": 15,
   "en": "I suppose there's no point hiding it."
  },
  {
   "i": 16,
   "en": "Eri, come to the meeting room?"
  },
  {
   "i": 17,
   "en": "Okay..."
  },
  {
   "i": 18,
   "en": "Huh? My CD sales..."
  },
  {
   "i": 19,
   "en": "aren't good?"
  },
  {
   "i": 20,
   "en": "No. I believe the song itself"
  },
  {
   "i": 21,
   "en": "turned out well, but..."
  },
  {
   "i": 22,
   "en": "somehow it isn't turning into numbers"
  },
  {
   "i": 23,
   "en": "As for why..."
  },
  {
   "i": 24,
   "en": "For one, not enough promotion."
  },
  {
   "i": 25,
   "en": "And also―㌍"
  },
  {
   "i": 26,
   "en": "And also...?"
  },
  {
   "i": 27,
   "en": "the rookie audition from before may"
  },
  {
   "i": 28,
   "en": "have hurt us a little, too"
  },
  {
   "i": 29,
   "en": "A win there would have been"
  },
  {
   "i": 30,
   "en": "good publicity"
  },
  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "I'm sorry..."
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "Don't apologize. Let's neither of us"
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "dwell on what's past"
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
   "en": "The biggest problem―㌍the CD sales"
  },
  {
   "i": 35,
   "en": "are hurting our next audition, too"
  },
  {
   "i": 36,
   "en": "Huh? The next one?"
  },
  {
   "i": 37,
   "en": "Yes. I can't secure us an entry"
  },
  {
   "i": 38,
   "en": "slot in any good auditions..."
  },
  {
   "i": 39,
   "en": "At this rate, we can't even find"
  },
  {
   "i": 40,
   "en": "a thread to start clawing back"
  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "So we need CD sales... no matter what?"
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "Right. No numbers, no way forward"
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "We can't afford to sit"
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "around waiting anymore"
  },
  {
   "i": 45,
   "en": "I'll go around the shops one by one"
  },
  {
   "i": 46,
   "en": "and ask them to push it hard"
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "You'd go that far?"
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "We do whatever it takes. So you"
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "be ready to eat some mud too, okay?"
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "You may end up taking on a few"
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "rougher jobs than usual"
  },
  {
   "i": 52,
   "en": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "i": 53,
   "en": "It's all... for the next audition?"
  },
  {
   "i": 54,
   "en": "That's right"
  },
  {
   "i": 55,
   "en": "...Got it"
  },
  {
   "i": 56,
   "en": "If my CD sales don't grow,"
  },
  {
   "i": 57,
   "en": "is this the end for us?"
  },
  {
   "i": 58,
   "en": "Isn't there something I can do?"
  },
  {
   "i": 59,
   "en": "Something that even I can do..."
  }
 ]
}